snippet.title: MIniclip: Stress Relief! Paintball Gameplay
snippet.description:
This was another very old Miniclip flash game, where you're in first-person shooter mode. You shoot as much yellow smile faces as you can in an office, and you get the scores you need. Totally addictive, wasn't it?

Platforms:
BlueMaxima's Flashpoint
Y8 Browser
------------------------------
By Bandicam Screen Recorder (https://www.bandicam.com)
